# Path-preserve all Substack-native URLs so links from past newsletters,
# RSS subscribers, and bookmarks keep working after we take over the
# domain at theairuntime.com.

/p/*           https://theairuntime.substack.com/p/:splat            301
/feed          https://theairuntime.substack.com/feed                301
/archive       https://theairuntime.substack.com/archive             301
/subscribe     https://theairuntime.substack.com/subscribe           301
/podcast       https://theairuntime.substack.com/podcast             301
/comments/*    https://theairuntime.substack.com/comments/:splat     301
/api/v1/*      https://theairuntime.substack.com/api/v1/:splat       301

# Bare root → publication. 302 (not 301) so we can change our minds later.
/              https://theairuntime.substack.com/                    302
